# 🚀 STEP 3 — Recreate StorageCluster (CRITICAL)

Now we recreate **same cluster**.

👉 Minimal working YAML (based on your setup):

```yaml
apiVersion: ocs.openshift.io/v1
kind: StorageCluster
metadata:
  name: ocs-storagecluster
  namespace: openshift-storage
spec:
  manageNodes: false
  monDataDirHostPath: /var/lib/rook
  storageDeviceSets:
  - name: ocs-deviceset
    count: 1
    replica: 3
    portable: false
    dataPVCTemplate:
      spec:
        accessModes:
        - ReadWriteOnce
        resources:
          requests:
            storage: 1000Gi
        storageClassName: localblock
        volumeMode: Block
```

